% Piecewise Linear Interpolation: PiecewiseLinearInterpolation.mod in https://www3.nd.edu/~jeff/mathprog/#
\text{maximize } f\\
\text{subject to } s_{n} \leq z_{n}: n \in 1 \ldots N\\
1 = \sum_{n \in 1 \ldots N} z_{n}\\
x = \sum_{n \in 1 \ldots N} (xi_{n-1}*z_{n} + (xi_{n}-xi_{n-1})*s_{n})\\
f = \sum_{n \in 1 \ldots N} (fi_{n-1}*z_{n} + (fi_{n}-fi_{n-1})*s_{n})\\
xi_{n}, fi_{n} : n \in 0 \ldots N\\
f, x \in \mathbb{R}; s_{n} \in \mathbb{R}^{+}; z_{n} \in \mathbb{B}\\
